data.description: This darling single story one owner home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, dining room, galley kitchen, fresh interior paint, updated LVP throughout, and an open floor plan perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is complete with SS appliances, custom backsplash, cabinets for plenty of storage and a walk in pantry. The primary suite offers great space to create your own retreat along with a walk in closet. The primary bath is complete with dual vanities and soaking tub. Perfect for first time homebuyers or families. This move in ready home won't last long!
